Algorithm steps
 	1)Right number of command line arguments has been provided:
 		No:
		Terminate.
		
 		Yes:
		2)Read text into String.
		3)Read line length.
		4)Tokenize String.
		5)Find length of each token.
		While tokens left:
			6)Calculate number of tokens per line
			7)Calculate number of spaces to add on the left side of each line
			7)Print right-aligned line